---
const stages = [
  ['Command Inbox','Only CEO B final research, blockers, and decisions. No noisy signal spam.'],
  ['Signal Review','Raw signals, watchlist moves, and agent findings. Easy to read, deeper details on click.'],
  ['Risk Gate','Omega Vault checks invalidation, downside, confidence, and duplicates before anything goes forward.'],
  ['Archive Route','Anything useful but not urgent gets saved to Archive instead of cluttering Command.'],
];
---
<html lang="en"><head><title>Staging — Pickaxe Capital</title><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" /><style>body{margin:0;background:#05070d;color:#eef4ff;font-family:Inter,system-ui,sans-serif}.wrap{padding:36px;min-height:100vh;background:radial-gradient(circle at top,#172247,#05070d 55%)}h1{font-size:44px;margin:0 0 8px}.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:18px;margin-top:28px}.card{border:1px solid rgba(122,151,218,.18);background:rgba(7,13,25,.8);border-radius:20px;padding:22px;min-height:220px;box-shadow:0 20px 70px #000}.card b{color:#f7b84b;font-size:20px}.card p{color:#aeb9ca;line-height:1.6}.lane{height:7px;border-radius:999px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#f7b84b,#a855f7,#20d3ff);margin-top:20px;animation:flow 3s linear infinite;background-size:200% 100%}@keyframes flow{to{background-position:200% 0}}@media(max-width:900px){.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}</style></head><body><main class="wrap"><h1>STAGING PAGE</h1><p>Separate page for Command + Signals so the main habitat stays clean.</p><section class="grid">{stages.map(s=><article class="card"><b>{s[0]}</b><p>{s[1]}</p><div class="lane"></div></article>)}</section></main></body></html>
